description: What lies beneath paper covered in New Year patterns? A warm and gentle surprise, or the fulfillment of a long cherished dream? Either way, it is a symbol of a miracle drawing near.[list][*]Limited Edition.[*]Don't drop in game.[*]Available for purchase in-store only.[/list]
